title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Law Enforcement Vehicle Discounts
content:
In addition to completing the first mission for The Cluckin’ Bell Farm Raid, you’ll need to own a decommissioned Law Enforcement Vehicle for Dispatch Work. Luckily, Warstock Cache & Carry is running a fire sale for the next two weeks.

Vapid Caracara Pursuit – 25% off
Bravado Gauntlet Interceptor – 35% off
Invetero Coquette D10 Pursuit – 25% off
Declasse Impaler LX Cruiser – 35% off
